sets.summary: Level up the intensity to build a broader, stronger back.
sets.subTitle: Centr Power in Gym: Advanced week 4

workouts.title: Workout
workouts.introText:
Luke and Chris have lined up a new set of lifts to dial up strength, size and definition in your back.


Set up your form with the tutorial, select your weights, then give it 100%.

groups.title: Warm-up
groups.summary: Switch on your muscles so you're ready to give it 100%.

groups.title: Round 1
groups.summary: Lock in good form to fully engage your posterior chain and support your lower back.

groups.title: Round 2
groups.summary: High reps and supersets will test your endurance.

groups.title: Round 3
groups.summary: Build a strong posture, row by row.

groups.title: Round 4
groups.summary: You've got high reps on this upper-back move, so keep it steady.
